People from the underground private bank were so cautious.

5
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:27,370
I was discovered in the end.

6
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:29,120
I've been hiding my real identity for so long.

7
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:31,120
But I didn't even see the mastermind.

8
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,320
However, I've heard that

9
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,920
the underground private bank's money laundering institution

10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,720
